STATE v. ROWE. No. COA05-566. North Carolina Court of Appeals. Filed January 3, 2006. Certification Date January 23, 2006. Appeal from Carteret (04CRS50432, 04CRS50433, 04CRS50434).

Case without published opinion. No error in pat, reversed and remanded for a new trial on the charge of attemped felonious breaking or entering.
